The '''Mos Eisley Police Authority''' was the local [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|law enforcement agency]] in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]], [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. Their force was armed with [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]] and had a [[Mos Eisley Police Station|station]] in the spaceport to enable the questioning of suspects. The [[Police officer/Legends|officers]] patrolled the city and also operated in space above Tatooine.

In [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]] the police force was tasked to bring in the unknown [[BoShek/Legends|pilot]] that ran an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] blockade in effect around the planet.

Among their number were guard [[Happer]], pilot [[Kelen Wordkal|Captain Wordkal]], an unidentified [[Mos Eisley cop|cop]]. Around the time of the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Harburik]] served as Chief of Police.

